Add_Dynamic_Module Input Appeal_SDL2_Input
Input Set_Paths ./Resources
Input Add_Control_Set Default
Input Set_Control_Set Default
Input Open_Controller -1
Input Bind_Button Confirm 0:Button_A
Input Bind_Axis Move_X 0:Left_Stick_X
Input Set_Controller_Button_Down_For 0 Button_A Player_One_Confirm
Input Set_Controller_Button_Up_For 0 Button_A Player_One_Release_Confirm
Input Set_Controller_Axis_For 0 Left_Stick_X Player_One_Move_X
Input Set_Controller_Axis_Range 0 Left_Stick_Y -12000 -4000 Player_One_Stealth_Forward
Input Set_Controller_Axis_Range 0 Left_Stick_Y -24000 -12001 Player_One_Walk_Forward
Input Set_Controller_Axis_Range 0 Left_Stick_Y -32768 -24001 Player_One_Run_Forward

Input Update Default
Print Hold_Button_A_Now
Delay 3
Input Update Default
Input Down Confirm
Input Pressed Confirm
Input Controller_Down 0 Button_A
Input Controller_Pressed 0 Button_A

Print Release_Button_A_Now
Delay 3
Input Update Default
Input Released Confirm
Input Controller_Released 0 Button_A

Print Move_Left_Stick_Right_Now
Delay 3
Input Update Default
Input Axis Move_X
Input Controller_Axis 0 Left_Stick_X

Print Move_Left_Stick_Forward_A_Little_Now
Delay 3
Input Update Default
Input Controller_Axis 0 Left_Stick_Y

Print Move_Left_Stick_Forward_Halfway_Now
Delay 3
Input Update Default
Input Controller_Axis 0 Left_Stick_Y

Print Move_Left_Stick_Forward_All_The_Way_Now
Delay 3
Input Update Default
Input Controller_Axis 0 Left_Stick_Y

Input Close_Controller -1
Done
